<div id="main_content">
	<h2>Energy Conservation Efforts Produce Substantial Savings</h2>
	
	<p class="article_info">
		
			By Chad Binette
		
		<span class="date">May 22, 2009</span></p>
	
	
	
		<div class="article_img" style="width: 345px;">

			<img alt="Article Main Picture" src="../resources/sites/UCF/content/live/NEWS/1000/NE1772/en_US/idafull.jpg" height="226" width="345"  /> 
			
				<p class="photo_credit">Photo: Jacque Brund</p>
			
			<p>Faculty Senate Chair Ida Cook receives a Pegasus pin from UCF President John Hitt during her first meeting as a Board of Trustees member.</p>
			
				<p class="note"><a class="full_photo" id="popup.jsp?article_id=00240041037381429012136c33d790076b5">Full Photo</a></p>
			
			
			
			
					
						
						
						
					
			
			
			
					
						
						
							
